<a name="belt_of_dwarf_slaying"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Belt of Dwarf Slaying - AC 20</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/waist.shtml">Waist</a><BR>
Weight: 0.0 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/bard/armour/waist.shtml">BRD</a>, <a href="/cleric/armour/waist.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/druid/armour/waist.shtml">DRU</a>, <a href="/enchanter/armour/waist.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/armour/waist.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/monk/armour/waist.shtml">MNK</a>, <a href="/necromancer/armour/waist.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/paladin/armour/waist.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/ranger/armour/waist.shtml">RNG</a>, <a href="/rogue/armour/waist.shtml">ROG</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/armour/waist.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/shaman/armour/waist.shtml">SHM</a>, <a href="/warrior/armour/waist.shtml">WAR</a>, <a href="/wizard/armour/waist.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/aura_of_battle.shtml?spellID=769">Aura of Battle</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(STR +15) (INT +15) (WIS +15) (Sv Magic +5) (Sv Cold +5) (Sv Fire +5) (Sv Poison +5) (Sv Disease +5) (HP +100) (Mana +100) </font>
<BR>
Obtained via a quest in Kael Drakkel.<BR>

